string-array.name: cardTitles
string-array.item: I am one of a kind
Each day is a new opportunity to grow and be a better version
Every challenge in my life is an opportunity to learn from
I have so much to be grateful for
Good things are always coming into my life
New opportunities await me at every turn
I have the courage to follow my heart
All my expectation will happen the right time
I will not miss my moment
Money will meet more in my hand
